text: Dancing master may refer to: * The Dancing Master, a dance manual, first published by John Playford in 1651 * Dancing master, an early term for a dance teacher, or perhaps a choreographer * The Compleat Dancing Master, a 1974 English folk rock album, by Ashley Hutchings with John Kirkpatrick and others * "Dancing Master", a song on John Entwistle's 1981 album Too Late the Hero ==See also== *Dance
title: Dancing master
